===Noun===
'''ornament''' (plural '''ornaments''')

#An element of decoration.
#''Music.'' a musical flourish that are unnecessary to the overall melodic or harmonic line, but serve to decorate or "ornament" that line. ([[w:Ornament (music)|Wikipedia article]]).

